cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with the segmentation of brain structures in ultrasound using a multi-scale fully convolutional neural network. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of weakly annotated labels and label transfer from MRI to US involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The use of synthetic US data for transfer learning also involves neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques.
